data.description: Amazing,  spacious 2-Story home in much desired  Bittersweet Subdivision.  Available for quick Closing - Be in your new home by Christmas.  Seller is offering a $3000 CONCESSION TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS OR A RATE BUY DOWN.  PLUS a 1 Year First American EAGLE PREMIER  HOME WARRANTY IS INCLUDED FOR BUYER.  This beautiful 5 BD, 4BA home boasts a dream kitchen with  stainless, granite, gas cooktop, double ovens, & more. Formal dining rm. on one side &  cozy family rm. with woodburning fireplace on the other. Off main level is an enclosed heated , all season Porch /Sunroom-  276-sq, ft-  of added living space for year round relaxation. The 90% finished large  L-Shaped basement rec. room  gives  space for more  entertaining..  Lots of storage space throughout.  The back yard holds a cozy patio with a gas firepit for enjoying cool evening outdoors. A storage shed gives added space for yard equipment. Buyer to verify measurements
